&lt;p&gt;Dental Nurse&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen within CLCH Community &amp; Specialist Dental Service for 1 year fixed term full time Band 5 Senior Dental Nurse&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These posts involve clinical nursing responsibilities in CDS and SDS based in multi-surgery clinics within the 3 inner London boroughs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit a proactive and enthusiastic Senior Dental Nurse to provide support, supervision and leadership within the Dental Nursing team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Post holders will actively support the Dental Nurse Manager and the Dental Nurse Team Leads to develop the Band 4 nurses in line with the ethos of the Trust and Dental Services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful applicant will support and deputise for the Dental Nurse Team Leads when required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Full training and support will be given to the post holder.&lt;/p&gt;
